window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"I was told to beware the accursed spindle, but it was so enchanting, so hypnotic....</p> <p>\"I was looking for a little adventure the day I ditched my tour group. But finding a comatose town, with a hot-looking chick asleep in it, was so not what I had in mind. </p> <p>\"I awakened in the same place but in another time – to a stranger’s soft kiss. I couldn’t help kissing her. Sometimes you just have to kiss someone. I didn’t know this would happen.</p> <p>\"Now I am in dire trouble because my father, the king, says I have brought ruin upon our country. I have no choice but to run away with this commoner!\"</p> <p><i>\"Now I’m stuck with a bratty princess and a trunk full of her jewels. The good news: My parents will freak!\"</i></p>"; 
